        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Rhodoliths bed, Pajara Islet, Cocos Island, at 22 m in depth. Photograph by Beatriz Naranjo, UCR." , "Figure 3. Rhodolitica occulta sp. nov., holotype MZUCR 2514 A, B outer coenenchymal sclerites C inner coenenchymal sclerites D anthocodial sclerites E tentacular sclerites F fused and partially fused sclerites from stolons, details at the right." , "Figure 2. Rhodolitica occulta sp. nov. A holotype MZUCR 2514 B paratype MZUCR 2513, ribbon-like stolons can be observed at the upper cluster of polyps (white arrows) C unsorted sclerites of the holotype D tentacular sclerites." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/532551" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/532550" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/532549" .

